{"word":"ἀσθενέω","slug":"ἀσθενέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀσθενέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀσθενής'><el>ἀσθενής</el></a>\n<p/><i>to be weak, feeble, sickly</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ἠσθένησε</el> <i>he fell sick</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/>"}]}